fields.title: Greek salad
fields.menu_item_description: A refreshing combination of crisp lettuce, juicy tomatoes, cucumber slices, red onions, tangy Kalamata olives, and creamy feta cheese, drizzled with extra virgin olive oil and sprinkled with oregano.

fields.title: Pasta with tomato and basil
fields.menu_item_description: Al dente pasta tossed in a savory tomato sauce infused with fragrant basil leaves, garnished with grated Parmesan cheese.

fields.title: Grilled fish
fields.menu_item_description: Fresh fillet of fish seasoned with herbs and spices, grilled to perfection, served with a side of steamed vegetables.

fields.title: Mediterranean salad
fields.menu_item_description: A vibrant mix of fresh lettuce, diced tomatoes, cucumber slices, red onions, black olives, and crumbled feta cheese, tossed in a zesty Mediterranean dressing.

fields.title: Lemon dessert
fields.menu_item_description: A luscious lemon cake with a moist and tender crumb, infused with tangy lemon flavor and topped with a sweet lemon glaze for the perfect balance of sweet and sour.

fields.title: Bruschetta
fields.menu_item_description: Crispy slices of toasted baguette topped with a flavorful mixture of diced ripe tomatoes, fresh basil, garlic, and extra virgin olive oil, finished with a sprinkle of balsamic glaze for a classic Italian appetizer.

fields.title: Pancake with sliced strawberry
fields.menu_item_description: Fluffy pancakes served with a generous portion of fresh strawberries sliced on top, drizzled with maple syrup for a delightful breakfast or dessert option.

fields.title: Fish salad
fields.menu_item_description: A light and healthy salad featuring flaky pieces of grilled fish on a bed of mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, and avocado slices, dressed with a zesty vinaigrette.

fields.title: Raspberry cake
fields.menu_item_description: Indulge in the decadent flavors of this moist and flavorful cake, filled with layers of rich raspberry filling and adorned with crunchy pistachio nuts, topped with fresh raspberries for a delightful contrast of textures and tastes.

fields.title: Toast bread with blueberry
fields.menu_item_description: Slices of toasted bread served with a generous spread of blueberry jam, perfect for a simple yet satisfying breakfast or snack option.

fields.title: Waffle with sliced strawberries and blueberries
fields.menu_item_description: Golden, fluffy waffles topped with a vibrant medley of sliced strawberries and blueberries, drizzled with maple syrup for a sweet and satisfying breakfast treat. This breakfast also includes a side of fresh apricots, adding a touch of sweetness and tartness to complement the waffles and fruit topping.

fields.title: Brownie
fields.menu_item_description: Rich and decadent, our classic brownie is baked to perfection with a fudgy texture and intense chocolate flavor, making it the ultimate indulgence for any sweet tooth.

fields.title: Cheesecake
fields.menu_item_description: Creamy and velvety, our cheesecake features a buttery graham cracker crust topped with a smooth and decadent cream cheese filling, offering a delightful balance of tangy sweetness in every bite.

fields.title: Ice cream with berries and jam
fields.menu_item_description: Indulge in a refreshing treat with our creamy vanilla ice cream, topped with a medley of fresh berries and a dollop of sweet jam, creating a harmonious blend of fruity flavors and creamy texture that's perfect for satisfying your sweet cravings.
